---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Research
description: Research themes in viral entry, antibody neutralization, and viral polymerase biology at the Abraham Lab.
permalink: /research/index.html
---
<section class="page-hero page-hero--light">
  <div class="container page-hero__content reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Research</p>
    <h1>Three connected scientific programs in viral infection biology.</h1>
    <p>
      The lab's work is organized around entry, neutralization, and replication. In each area, structural and
      mechanistic detail is used to identify leverage points for antiviral intervention.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="container page-hero__meta reveal">
    <div>
      <span>Core systems</span>
      <p>alphaviruses, arenaviruses, herpesviruses, and other medically significant viral families</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span>Core methods</span>
      <p>cryo-EM, crystallography, protein biochemistry, genetics, and infection-focused functional assays</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span>Program aim</span>
      <p>mechanistic resolution of therapeutic vulnerability in human viral disease</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--bordered">
  <div class="container program-list">
    {% for item in research %}
      <article class="program-block reveal">
        <div class="program-block__visual">
          <img src="{{ item.image | withBase }}" alt="{{ item.imageAlt }}" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="program-block__content">
          <p class="eyebrow">{{ ("0" + loop.index) if loop.index < 10 else loop.index }}</p>
          <h2>{{ item.title }}</h2>
          <p class="program-block__importance">{{ item.importance }}</p>
          <p class="program-block__summary">{{ item.summary }}</p>
          {% for paragraph in item.paragraphs %}
            <p>{{ paragraph }}</p>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <aside class="program-block__meta">
          <div class="meta-block">
            <span>Program focus</span>
            <p>{{ item.lead }}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-block">
            <span>Representative systems</span>
            <ul class="clean-list">
              {% for system in item.systems %}
                <li>{{ system }}</li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-block">
            <span>Representative methods</span>
            <ul class="clean-list">
              {% for method in item.methods %}
                <li>{{ method }}</li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-block">
            <span>Representative paper</span>
            <p><a href="{{ item.relatedLink }}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">{{ item.relatedPublication }}</a></p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--offwhite">
  <div class="container methodology-band reveal">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Approach</p>
      <h2>Integrated structure, biophysics, and infection biology.</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p>
        The Abraham Lab connects molecular structure with biological consequence through an experimental
        program that spans discovery genetics, protein science, structural analysis, and infection-focused
        assays.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="methodology-band__list">
      <p>CRISPR-based discovery</p>
      <p>Protein biochemistry</p>
      <p>Cryo-EM and crystallography</p>
      <p>Functional virology</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
